N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 7905.4 - Reports on compliance

State Regulations

The Commissioner of the State Energy Office may, by
written order served by mail, require any prime supplier or wholesale
purchaser-reseller to report concerning compliance with the provisions of this
subchapter and with any order issued pursuant thereto. Notes
